<h1>Hello World</h1>
<address>
Albert Y. C. Lai
</address>

<p>Save this in a file named "hello1.hs".</p>

<pre>main = putStrLn "hello world"
</pre>

<p>To run it, enter this at a shell prompt:</p>

<pre>$ runghc hello1.hs
</pre>

<p>Or, enter this at a GHCi prompt:</p>

<pre>Prelude&gt; :load hello1.hs
*Main&gt; main
</pre>

<p>Just for the kick, here is another version, "hello2.hs"</p>

<pre><![CDATA[main = interact (const "hello world\n")
]]></pre>

</body>
</html>
